it  became  a  killer  app  of  links , and  today , of  course , we  call  that  the  world  wide  web .
now , not  only  was  i  instrumental  in  helping  apple  miss  the  internet , but  a  couple  of  years  later , i  helped  bill  gates  do  the  same  thing .
the  year  is  1993 .
and  he  was  working  on  a  book  and  i  was  working  on  a  video  to  help  him  kind  of  explain  where  we  were  all  heading  and  how  to  popularize  all  this .
