you  know ? so  you  also  have  the  ability  for  people  to  start  coming  together  and  acting  on  their  own  behalf  in  political  and  civic  ways .
in  ways  that  have  n't  happened  before .
and  as  we  heard  last  night , as  we've  heard  earlier  this  week , are  absolutely , fundamentally  vital  to  the  ability  to  craft  new  solutions , is  we've  got  to  craft  new  political  realities .
and  i  would  personally  say  that  we  have  to  craft  new  political  realities , not  only  in  places  like  india , afghanistan , kenya , pakistan , what  have  you , but  here  at  home  as  well .
another  world  is  possible .
and  sort  of  the  big  motto  of  the  anti-globalization  movement .
right ? we  tweak  that  a  lot .
