just  very  quickly  to  say  that  my  point  really  here , is  that  while  we’re  making  all  these  huge  advancements , what  we  're  doing , which  for  me , you  know , i  think  we  should , africa  should  move  forward , but  we  should  remember , so  we  do  not  go  back  here  again .
