so  are  you  saying  that  we  should  think  of  the  universe , at  its  heart , that  the  smallest  things  that  there  are , are  somehow  an  e8  object  of  possibility ? i  mean , is  there  a  scale  to  it , at  the  smallest  scale , or  gl , well , right  now  the  pattern  i  showed  you  that  corresponds  to  what  we  know  about  elementary  particle  physics , that  already  corresponds  to  a  very  beautiful  shape .
and  that  's  the  one  that  i  said  we  knew  for  certain .
